                     <interp inst="t18450407-1025-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>stealing 80 lbs. weight of coals, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450407-name-1308" type="victimName">
