                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable L</hi> 178.) I produce a certificate of Heath's former conviction, which I got from the Sessions-house, Surrey—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 18th March, 1844, confined three months, and whipped.</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
